<div class="sg-buttons">
  {% for type in button_types %}
    <table class="sg-buttons-type">
      <thead><caption class="sg-buttons-type-label">{{ type | replace({'type-': ''}) }}</caption>
      <tr>
        <th></th>
      {% for size in button_sizes %}
        <th>{{ size | replace({'size-': ''}) }}</th>
      {% endfor %}
      </tr>
      </thead>
      <tr>
        <td class="sg-buttons-type-row-label">No icon</td>
        {% for size in button_sizes %}
          <td class="sg-buttons-type-row-cell">{% include '@atoms/30-button/button.twig' with { button_text: 'Donate now', button_modifiers: [type, size] } only %}</td>
        {% endfor %}
      <tr>
        <td class="sg-buttons-type-row-label">With icon</td>
        {% for size in button_sizes %}
          <td class="sg-buttons-type-row-cell">{% include '@atoms/30-button/button.twig' with { button_text: 'Donate now', button_icon_name: 'caret-right', button_modifiers: [type, size] } only %}</td>
        {% endfor %}
      </tr>
    </table>
  {% endfor %}
</div>

<h3 class="sg-buttons-type-label">Button within hot container</h3>
<p>This demonstrates the usage of a button within a container that is a link. In this scenario the button's hover effect needs to fire whenever the hot container is hovered into.</p>
<p style="margin-bottom: 2rem">Implementation note: Add an attribute to the containing link called <span style="font-family: monospace;">data-rpla-hover-target</span>. HTML does not permit links within links, so it is important not to attempt to use the anchor tag for your button when you are within a hot container.</p>
<a style='margin-bottom: 2rem;' href="#" class="sg-buttons-hot-container" data-rpla-hover-target>
  <h3 class="rpla-heading rpla-heading--medium">Donec mollis hendrerit</h3>
  <p class="rpla-paragraph">Maecenas vestibulum mollis diam. Donec mollis hendrerit risus. Etiam ultricies nisi vel augue. Quisque malesuada placerat nisl. Praesent porttitor, nulla vitae posuere iaculis, arcu nisl dignissim dolor, a pretium mi sem ut ipsum.</p>
  {% include '@atoms/30-button/button.twig' with { button_icon_name: 'heart', button_text: 'Donate now' } only %}
</a>

